title: How to Control Your Brain
itunes:title: How to Control Your Brain
description:
Episode 435 - I would estimate that 90% of people never take control of their brains, they just let it run wild and never fully harness the power of their minds. In this episode I will teach you how to master your mind so that you can create the life that you want.
